    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a solid candidate for a restoration or a dedicated parts car. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
